{
  "stem": "3835.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I should do with her the business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was the only one allowed to come into the store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a good looking woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was a lover from the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they gave her a gift.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They gave her three Jewish-- no, a Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[POLISH] was her name, [POLISH], [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was-- she had three stores, a few Jews-- as many as she wants, I think she could get.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But and so she picked our store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her headquarters was in our store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she took me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she gave me papers that I work for her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And naturally, she was a bridge player too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the weekends, when we were closed-- Sunday we were closed, the stores, I spent the whole day in her house to play bridge.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sometimes, I played till 2, 12 o'clock midnight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a Jew couldn't walk more than, I think, 8:00 or 9:00-- whatever the curfew was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I came once back from her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was about 12 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And who is going on the same side?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[GERMAN], one of the Gestapo, with his dog, which was taller than I was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And naturally, I stopped right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Show me your papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I showed him my papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, you can go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If I wouldn't have the papers, either I got shot to death or-- he wouldn't bother to arrest me, at least not right away in the-- Were there other restrictions besides this curfew on Jews?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This came later, later after this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As the time passed by, it started to be worse and worse for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- people which they were living outside of the town had to come to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
